         <div type="translation">
            <p>Polydeukes, Castor, Athena Alea. God. Resolved by the people. Ergoteles was archon,
               Ismeinias proposed. Let Timea[s] son of Cheirikrates the Lakonian be pro[xenos] and
               benefacto[r of the Boio]tians, both him and his descen[dants] and let him have the
               right to (purchase) land a[nd a house]...</p></div>
         
